name: Goobercoin #3
description:
All profits are split between filmmaker and skater. 
This clip features my friend Anderson, who is from the favelas of Brazil and grinds hard in America in pursuit of his dream of going pro. 

This trick was filmed at Pier 7 in San Francisco, a famous walkway along the bay to Alcatraz Island. This spot also played a fundamental role in the development of modern street skateboarding and is a rite of passage for every skater who wants to go pro.
